30
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,310
I don't want to go in anymore.

31
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,510
I once truly hoped

32
00:01:34,510 --> 00:01:35,920
that you were Zixing,

33
00:01:36,430 --> 00:01:38,400
because I had been longing for his return.

34
00:01:39,500 --> 00:01:41,350
But now, I'd rather you weren't him.

35
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,610
Someone as wonderful as him

36
00:01:46,430 --> 00:01:49,230
could never turn into a monster like you.

37
00:01:49,630 --> 00:01:51,350
I don't know what kind of person

38
00:01:51,350 --> 00:01:52,430
this Li Zixing you speak of was,

39
00:01:54,870 --> 00:01:56,120
but from today on,

40
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,040
you can consider him

41
00:01:59,230 --> 00:02:00,430
dead.

42
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:01,630
He's gone.

43
00:02:01,990 --> 00:02:04,710
