57
00:02:38,670 --> 00:02:40,110
will never disappear.

58
00:02:40,920 --> 00:02:43,510
I'd rather you never have to experience this pain.

59
00:02:44,430 --> 00:02:45,280
Leave now.

60
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:48,040
My journey ahead is full of danger,

61
00:02:49,110 --> 00:02:50,230
and no matter what,

62
